text: No patient was excluded because of missing data . P < 0 . 05 was considered significant ; all tests were bilateral , and statistical analysis was conducted with Stata version 13 . 0 ( Stata Corp . ) . With at least 100 cases and 100 controls , analyses had 80 % power to detect odds ratios ( OR ) ! 3 with ! 20 % prevalence of control exposure , whatever the prevalence of case exposure .
